Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耶ー！太棒了！（хороший）
